experience gained in the most important companies in the industry, capable of transmitting <strong>visual strategies</strong> and aesthetic principles of the brand in line with current corporate standards to enhance your <strong>aesthetic sensitivity</strong> and express your<strong> creative and communicative abilities</strong> to the fullest.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"course-structure\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Course Structure</strong></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]The course aims to train a highly qualified figure in the field of visual and digital communication, capable of using appropriate languages and tools to anticipate and meet customer requests through their vision of fashion and aesthetic taste. The course aims to ensure adequate mastery of artistic methods and techniques, as well as the acquisition of specific disciplinary and professional skills, to provide students with design and expressive knowledge and methodologies in the use of representation tools and artistic practices, with particular attention to fashion.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"admissions\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"84\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%