(66, 1, '2025-05-30 18:48:07', '2025-05-30 16:48:07', '[vc_row width=\"full\" css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22background-color%22%3A%22%23E9E9E9%22%2C%22margin-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-right%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%220%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"49\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>The Bachelor of Arts with Honours in Fashion Business and Psychology, integrates the study of business and neuromarketing within the context of the fashion industry.</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"overview\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22font-size%22%3A%221.5rem%21important%22%7D%7D\"]\r\n<h3><strong>Overview</strong></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]It provides a comprehensive view of the fashion system and emphasizes the role of <strong>consumer psychology</strong> in the marketing strategies of fashion and luxury companies. Led by expert lecturers and utilizing <strong>state-of-the-art technology</strong>, this multidisciplinary course offers a practical and innovative experience. Transform your career in the fashion industry, where <strong>creativity and neuroscience</strong> converge to define the <strong>future of business</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis course is validated by Teesside University, which will award the degree upon completion of the program.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"course-structure\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Course Structure</strong></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]The course aims to offer a robust education in the field of <strong>fashion business</strong>, seamlessly integrated with insights into neuromarketing. Students will acquire multidisciplinary skills to comprehend consumer behavior by applying <strong>neuroscientific principles</strong> to marketing strategies in the <strong>fashion industry</strong>. Educational objectives include the ability to analyze neuroscientific data, develop innovative branding strategies, and understand the <strong>psychological dynamics</strong> that drive purchasing decisions.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"admissions\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"89\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding