(71, 1, '2025-05-30 18:50:41', '2025-05-30 16:50:41', '[vc_row width=\"full\" css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22background-color%22%3A%22%23E9E9E9%22%2C%22margin-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-right%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%220%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"49\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Milano ModaLab is a summer camp aimed at young international and Italian students who want to live a unique experience in Milano and explore different disciplines: drawing, design, styling, and communication in one of the most prestigious Fashion Schools in Italy, whilst enriching their education and curriculum.</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"overview\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22font-size%22%3A%221.5rem%21important%22%7D%7D\"]\r\n<h3><strong>Overview</strong></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]Milano ModaLab is an intensive two-week programme designed for fashion enthusiasts and aspiring designers and creatives. Hosted in Milan, the global fashion capital, this course offers a unique blend of hands-on workshops, expert-led lectures, and exclusive visits to renowned fashion houses and ateliers.\r\n\r\nParticipants explore key aspects of the fashion industry, including trend forecasting, how the fashion system works, design &amp; garment construction, styling &amp; photography, fashion comunication. With guidance from fashion professionals, students gain insights into the latest trends, sustainable practices, and the creative processes that drive the world of contemporary fashion.\r\n\r\nThroughout the programme, participants work on different projects, culminating in a presentation where they can showcase their portfolio. Milano Moda Lab is perfect for those looking to enhance their skills and get inspired by the vibrant culture and lifestyle of Milanese fashion.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"course-structure\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Course Structure</strong></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Milano ModaLab', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'milano-modalab', '', '', '2025-05-30 20:08:30', '2025-05-30 18:08:30', '', 70, 'http://localhost:8888/ferrarinew/?post_type=corsi&#038;p=71', 0, 'corsi', '', 0),
