 Director</li>\r\n 	<li>Art Director</li>\r\n 	<li>Image Consultant</li>\r\n 	<li>Content Creator</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Fashion Styling and Art Direction', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fashion-styling-and-art-direction', '', '', '2025-05-30 20:20:26', '2025-05-30 18:20:26', '', 72, 'http://localhost:8888/ferrarinew/?post_type=corsi&#038;p=73', 0, 'corsi', '', 0);
