(83, 1, '2025-05-30 19:28:11', '2025-05-30 17:28:11', '<p>[vc_row width=\"full\" css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22background-color%22%3A%22%23E9E9E9%22%2C%22margin-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-right%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%220%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"49\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h2>Become a professional in the fashion industry capable of designing and coordinating the communication of fashion brands and companies.</h2>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"overview\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22font-size%22%3A%221.5rem%21important%22%7D%7D\"]</p>\n<h3><strong>Overview</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]The course aims to provide design and methodological knowledge, research, graphic and visual design, aimed at a full understanding of current <strong>fashion trends</strong>, the most famous and prestigious brands on the international scene. Meet professors with strong academic and professional experience gained in the most important companies in the industry, capable of transmitting <strong>visual strategies</strong> and aesthetic principles of the brand in line with current corporate standards to enhance your <strong>aesthetic sensitivity</strong> and express your<strong> creative and communicative abilities</strong> to the fullest.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"course-structure\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Course Structure</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]The course aims to train a highly qualified figure in the field of visual and digital communication, capable of using appropriate languages and tools to anticipate and meet customer requests through their vision of fashion and aesthetic taste. The course aims to ensure adequate mastery of artistic methods and techniques, as well as the acquisition of specific disciplinary and professional skills, to provide students with design and expressive knowledge and methodologies in the use of representation tools and artistic practices, with particular attention to fashion.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"admissions\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"84\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"careers-opportunity\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Careers opportunity</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiVGJaRWdSQTBZdlVuWnRqcnZrbzdURiIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjQ0MjYwNTM0NSwiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\"></span><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiVGJaRWdSQTBZdlVuWnRqcnZrbzdURiIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjEwOTg4MjU4MywiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\"></span><span data-buffer=\"<!--(figma)(/figma)-->\"></span><span>Fashion Stylist</span></li>\n<li>Art Director</li>\n<li>Image Consultant</li>\n<li>Content Creator</li>\n<li>Fashion Editor</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"study-plan\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Study Plan</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_tta_accordion c_icon=\"plus\"][vc_tta_section title=\"First Year\" tab_link=\"%7B%22url%22%3A%22%22%7D\" active=\"1\"][vc_column_text]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Second Year\" tab_link=\"%7B%22url%22%3A%22%22%7D\"][vc_column_text]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetu