(88, 1, '2025-05-30 19:35:33', '2025-05-30 17:35:33', '<p>[vc_row width=\"full\" css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22background-color%22%3A%22%23E9E9E9%22%2C%22margin-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-right%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%220%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"49\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h2>The Bachelor of Arts with Honours in Fashion Business and Digital Marketing, integrates the study of business and digital marketing within the context of the fashion industry.</h2>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"overview\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22font-size%22%3A%221.5rem%21important%22%7D%7D\"]</p>\n<h3><strong>Overview</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]The course is designed to provide students with a holistic perspective on the fashion system, highlighting the fundamental role of <strong>digital</strong> in the marketing strategies of leading fashion companies. Students will engage with lecturers possessing robust academic and professional backgrounds gained in prominent <strong>fashion companies</strong>, enabling them to convey knowledge and methodologies aligned with current <strong>corporate standards</strong>.</p>\n<p>This course is validated by Teesside University, which will award the degree upon completion of the program.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"course-structure\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Course Structure</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]The course aims to equip students with industry-specific knowledge and academic skills, including research, digital literacy, business acumen, trend forecasting skills, and <strong>strategic thinking</strong>. It is built upon the innovative integration of <strong>business management principles</strong>, digital marketing, and <strong>brand management</strong> tools and techniques. Additionally, it offers a comprehensive understanding of <strong>business models</strong>, <strong>marketing strategies</strong>, and <strong>communication</strong> tools applied to the fashion industry.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"admissions\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"84\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3