can put themselves to the test, improve their language knowledge, get to know a National academic excellence and create professional relationships with the lecturers.</p>\n<p>Five different subjects are provided: Italian language and culture, writing workshop, history of art, design and Italian style, specific course in photography, video, fashion and design, a final test and a PLIDA certification.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"course-structure\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Course Structure</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<span data-metadata=\"&lt;!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiVGJaRWdSQTBZdlVuWnRqcnZrbzdURiIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjQ0MjYwNTM0NSwiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)--&gt;\"></span><span data-metadata=\"&lt;!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiVGJaRWdSQTBZdlVuWnRqcnZrbzdURiIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjEwOTg4MjU4MywiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)--&gt;\"></span><span data-buffer=\"&lt;!--(figma)(/figma)--&gt;\"></span><span>l corso mira a fornire una solida padronanza delle tecniche artistiche e competenze specifiche nel settore moda. Gli studenti acquisiranno conoscenze progettuali ed espressive, oltre a comprendere le dinamiche del sistema moda a livello nazionale e internazionale. Il programma include lo sviluppo di competenze metodologiche e tecniche per la progettazione di prodotti tessili, abbigliamento e accessori.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"admissions\"][vc_colu