(99, 1, '2025-05-30 20:18:37', '2025-05-30 18:18:37', '<p>[vc_row width=\"full\" css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22background-color%22%3A%22%23E9E9E9%22%2C%22margin-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22margin-right%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-left%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-top%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-bottom%22%3A%220%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%220%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][templatera id=\"49\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h2>Explore the realms of style, design, and visual storytelling. If you aspire to become a Fashion Stylist or Art Director with a leading creative force in the fashion industry, the Master in Fashion Stylist and Art Direction will provide you with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in this highly competitive field.</h2>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"overview\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22font-size%22%3A%221.5rem%21important%22%7D%7D\"]</p>\n<h3><strong>Overview</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]The combination of <strong>styling and fashion shooting</strong> makes this program unique and specific, as through practical and theoretical training, you will learn the art of curating distinctive looks, creating compelling fashion narratives, and developing a keen eye for aesthetics.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"course-structure\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Course Structure</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]The masterâs program aims to elevate the quality and <strong>excellence of fashion styling</strong>. The primary goal is to cultivate in students the ability to use sophisticated languages and tools, aimed at anticipating and exceeding client expectations through a refined <strong>vision of fashion and a distinctive aesthetic taste</strong>. The educational pillars of the Master in Fashion Styling and Art Direction focus on a deep understanding of the dynamics of the fashion system, both nationally and globally. At the same time, the program aims to equip students with advanced methodological and instrumental skills essential for the design of visual communication strategies involving individuals, models, celebrities, or fashion companies, serving as authentic vehicles of corporate representation in a contemporary high-level context. Furthermore, the course provides a full awareness of fashion <strong>shootings</strong>, refining the ability to effectively <strong>manage</strong> and direct photo sessions in the context of fashion.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"admissions\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Admissions</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_row_inner css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22background-color%22%3A%22_light_blue%22%2C%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-top%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-bottom%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Minimum age 21 years</span></li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Knowledge of graphic software (Photoshop)</span></li>\n<li><span>Previous academic and/or work experience in Fashion or Design areas.</span></li>\n<li><span>Additionally, a motivational letter, a portfolio (if available), and participation in an admission interview are required.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"careers-opportunity\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Careers opportunity</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span data-metadata=\"&lt;!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiVGJaRWdSQTBZdlVuWnRqcnZrbzdURiIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjQ0MjYwNTM0NSwiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)--&gt;\"></span><span data-metadata=\"&lt;!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiVGJaRWdSQTBZdlVuWnRqcnZrbzdURiIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjEwOTg4MjU4MywiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)--&gt;\"></span><span data-buffer=\"&lt;!--(figma)(/figma)--&gt;\"></span><span>Fashion Designer</span></li>\n<li>Fashion Brand Founder</li>\n<li>Creative Director</li>\n<li>Product Designer</li>\n<li>Design Director</li>\n<li>Cool Hunter</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\"%7B%22default%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22laptops%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%22%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22tablets%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%2C%22mobiles%22%3A%7B%22padding-left%22%3A%222.5rem%22%2C%22padding-right%22%3A%222.5rem%22%7D%7D\" el_id=\"study-plan\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3><strong>Study Plan</strong></h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_tta_accordion c_icon=\"plus\"][vc_tta_section title=\"Primo Anno\" tab_link=\"%7B%22url%22%3A%22%22%7D\" active=\"1\"][vc_column_text]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Secondo Anno\" tab_link=\"%7B%22url%22%3A%22%22%7D\"][vc_column_text]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Terzo Anno\" tab_link=\"%7B%22url%22%3A%22%22%7D\"][vc_column_text]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'Fashion Styling and Art Direction', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '73-autosave-v1', '', '', '2025-05-30 20:18:37', '2025-05-30 18:18:37', '', 73, 'http://localhost:8888/ferrarinew/?p=99', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
