(165, 12, '2024-11-28 12:38:29', '2024-11-28 11:38:29', 'Ferrari Fashion School hosted a Career Day with the BasicNet Group on Tuesday, October 29th, offering students a unique opportunity to explore career possibilities not only in the world of fashion but also in streetwear and lifestyle. During the event, Genesis Alva Bringas, Talent Acquisition, and Giulia Guglielminotti, Lifestyle Designer in Chief at Kappa, shared their experiences, providing valuable advice for building a successful career in a dynamic and evolving sector like BasicNet.\r\nCareer Day with BasicNet\r\nDuring the Career Day, Genesis Alva Bringas, Talent Acquisition, shared the story and evolution of the BasicNet Group, offering students valuable insights on how to approach the job market. She highlighted the key points for creating an effective resume and provided useful tips for successfully navigating the selection process. Through interactive QR codes, students could respond to questions and reflect on the core skills needed to succeed in the industry, making the experience even more engaging and educational.\r\n\r\nGiulia Guglielminotti, on the other hand, shared her professional experience, giving students a direct look into her role as Lifestyle Designer in Chief at Kappa. With passion and expertise, she illustrated the characteristics of her daily work, explaining how her role fits within a dynamic team and in a constantly evolving environment.\r\nWhy Career Days important?\r\nFor students, active participation in Career Days is essential, as these events provide a unique opportunity to connect directly with leading companies in the sector and gain insights into career opportunities and the skills required by the market. Asking questions and interacting with professionals allows students to delve into specific aspects of different careers and receive practical advice from industry experts.\r\n\r\nTaking an active role in these events helps students build confidence in professional relationships and gain a clearer vision of the path that awaits them after completing their studies.', 'Ferrari Fashion School is hosting the Career Day with GUess', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ferrari-fashion-school-is-hosting-the-career-day-with-guess', '', '', '2024-11-28 14:23:38', '2024-11-28 13:23:38', '', 0, 'https://ferrarifashionschool.it/?p=11388', 0, 'news', '', 0),
