(178, 3, '2019-12-23 16:49:44', '2019-12-23 15:49:44', '\r\n\r\n\r\nOn the past Friday, June 29th at 11 AM, at Palazzo Pirelli â site of Regione Lombardia in the Gonfalone Room, we held the official closing ceremony for the Academic Year 2017/2018 and the delivery of the Diploma to all the students from Ferrari Fashion School, who had ended their study path this year.\r\n\r\nWe decided to celebrate this important moment together with our students, their families and our staff with an official ceremony, sponsored by Regione Lombardia, with the purpose of giving value and promoting young talents in the field of Fashion and Design, thanks to whom Italy and Italian know-how is recognized as an excellence all over the world.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThese have been years of hard work and great satisfactions, for both our staff and all our students, who started together with us with effort and resolution an path of education, personal and professional growth.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt is, thus, our pride to celebrate the end of this path and wish them a long and brilliant career.\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Graduation 2018', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'graduation-2018', '', '', '2019-12-23 16:49:44', '2019-12-23 15:49:44', '', 0, 'https://www.ferrarifashionschool.it/?p=3096', 0, 'news', '', 0),
