(200, 12, '2024-07-24 17:18:39', '2024-07-24 15:18:39', 'Ferrari Fashion School hosted a guest talk with the Iranian designers of Pairi Daeza, a duo that is revolutionizing the fashion world by blending the rich Iranian cultural tradition with Italian fashion innovation.\r\n\r\nThe event, held at our premises, saw a large turnout of students eager to learn about the experiences and creative journey of these two extraordinary artists. The founders of Pairi Daeza, known for their ability to combine exquisite fabrics and millennia-old stories with modern design trends, shared their vision and commitment to promoting Iranian culture through fashion.\r\n\r\nDuring the event, the designers discussed the importance of Iranian tradition in their collections, highlighting how each garment they create represents a journey through Iran\'s history and art. They also spoke about the role of women in Iranian society and how this influences their work, creating pieces that celebrate feminine strength and beauty.\r\n\r\nOne of the most significant moments of the event was when the designers encouraged students to ask questions and express their doubts about the creative process behind creating a collection. This open dialogue allowed for an in-depth discussion on crucial topics such as material selection, sourcing inspiration, and the challenges of balancing tradition and modernity.\r\n\r\nThe words and experiences of the Pairi Daeza designers inspired participants, bringing a renewed enthusiasm for their own journey in the fashion world.\r\n\r\n', 'Meeting with Pairi Daeza Designers at Ferrari Fashion School', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'meeting-with-pairi-daeza-designers', '', '', '2024-11-18 17:08:11', '2024-11-18 16:08:11', '', 0, 'https://ferrarifashionschool.it/?p=10648', 0, 'news', '', 0),
