(209, 3, '2019-12-19 09:22:16', '2019-12-19 08:22:16', '\r\nMAY 13th 2019\r\nOur students at work for Apriti Moda 2019!\r\nDuring May Saturday 18th and Sunday 19th, Cinzia Sassoâs conception âApriti Modaâ revealed for free the secrets hidden in the ateliers.\r\n\r\nThe most important Maison, such as Armani, Versace, Trussardi, Fondazione Gianfranco FerrÃ¨, Herno, Laboratori Scala, Alberta Ferretti, Prada, Moncler, Zegna, Marras, Agnona, Cuccinelli, Curiel, Ricami, opened the door of the most wonderful royal palaces, of renewed factories and in the most beautiful alleys in Milan, in order to facilitate the public in getting to know the Fashion Industry, who is usually unaware of this world, which is usually open to few people, usually restricted authorized personnel.\r\n\r\nIn the capital city of the Fuorisalone, of PianoCity, BookCity, Apriti Moda celebrates the beginning of a new relationship between who creates and who lives Fashion in the City.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn this context, the commitment of our students was fundamental, both Italian and international, with different tasks: from the welcome service, to expert guide in the different Maison by telling the most secret stories, to managing the incoming visitors, as to creating daily contents and reports about the attendance at the event.\r\n\r\nThe main purpose was, as for many years until now, is to involve visitors into this experience, helping them appreciate an apparently close reality, which is actually both intimate and mysterious.\r\n\r\nWe are so proud of our Made in Italy, of the cultural and educational opportunities given to our students and we are sure in a long-lasting collaboration and growing project together with the companies from the field.', 'Our students at work for Apriti Moda 2019!', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Maecenas a ex ullamcorper nunc consequat scelerisque. Donec eu massa risus. Fusce purus nisi, lacinia vel congue sit amet, porta id urna. ', 'p