(259, 1, '2019-03-19 16:01:15', '2019-03-19 15:01:15', '\r\nDesign di Accessori\r\n\r\nIl corso in breve:\r\n\r\n 	Sede: Milano\r\n 	Durata: 1 anno\r\n 	Inizio: 1Â Ottobre 2022\r\n\r\n\r\nTi appassiona il mondo degli accessori?\r\nCon questo Master diventerai Designer e Tecnico specializzato in accessori della Moda e del Lusso.\r\nAttraverso lezioni teoriche e pratiche ti forniremo gli strumenti e le conoscenze per saper progettare e sviluppare autonomamente una collezione Uomo/Donna, di calzature, borse e accessori.\r\n\r\nParteciperai alle piÃ¹ importanti fiere di settore (MICAM, MIPEL, LINEA PELLE) incontrando professionisti, artigiani e tecnici del settore, per toccare con mano tutti gli aspetti della progettazione e realizzazione del prodotto.RICHIEDI INFORMAZIONI\r\nCaratteristiche del Master in Design di Accessori\r\n\r\nDESTINATARI\r\nDEL CORSO\r\n\r\nIl Corso si rivolge ai maggiori di 21 anni che abbiano giÃ  maturato esperienza di studio o equivalente esperienza lavorativa nellâarea del Fashion Design.\r\nSi accede previa valutazione di un portfolio artistico e colloquio motivazionale e conoscitivo.\r\nLa commissione si riserva di richiedere discrezionalmente di effettuare una prova di ammissione per verificare le capacitÃ .\r\n\r\nOBIETTIVI\r\nFORMATIVI\r\n\r\nIl programma di studi permette allo studente di intraprendere un percorso che lo porterÃ  a sviluppare la propria identitÃ  stilistica e una personale capacitÃ  creativa, comprendendo al meglio le metodologie di ricerca e le tecniche di progettazione e realizzazione dellâaccessorio di moda.\r\n\r\nLABORATORI\r\nE MATERIALE\r\nDIDATTICO\r\n\r\nLe attivitÃ  di Laboratorio ti permettono di realizzare prototipi, campioni o intere collezioni, appoggiandoti a Laboratori Artigiani esterni, convenzionati con la Scuola a prezzi agevolati. Il costo di prototipazione e produzione Ã¨ a carico dello studente e varia a seconda della tipologia di prodotto, dalla scelta dei materiali e dal numero di pezzi e verrÃ  concordato direttamente tra lo studente e il Laboratorio con il quale deciderÃ  di collaborare.\r\nI lavori migliori verranno poi selezionati e presentati durante Eventi di Moda, permettendo ai vincitori di collaborare con gli stilisti per partecipare alla sfilata di fine anno presentando la collezione accessori.\r\nIl materiale didattico viene fornito gratuitamente a tutti i nostri studenti e comprende:\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Libro di testo\r\n 	Dispense (cartacee e digitali)\r\n 	Schede tecniche prodotto\r\n 	Campionatura pellami e fodere\r\n 	Dime\r\n 	Basi\r\n\r\nRICHIEDI \r\nRICHIEDI INFORMAZIONI\r\nCompila il form, ti ricontatteremo il prima possibile.\r\nPreferisci parlare direttamente con il nostro Team di orientamento ?\r\nClicca qui e prenota un colloquio personalizzato .\r\', 'Design di Accessori', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'accessory-bags-shoes-design', '', '', '2022-07-25 15:55:11', '2022-07-25 13:55:11', '', 12, 'https://www.ferrarifashionschool.it/?page_id=27', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(260, 1, '2019-03-19 16:02:06', '2019-03-19 15:02:06', '\r\n3 Year Course\r\nFashion Styling\r\nand Communication\r\n\r\nCourse Details\r\nLocation: Milan\r\n\r\nDuration: 3 academic years\r\n\r\nStart: October 2025\r\n\r\nCredits: 180\r\n\r\nClass size: max 15 students\r\n\r\nLanguage: Italian\r\nBecome a professional in the fashion industry capable of designing and coordinating the communication of fashion brands and companies.\r\nThe course aims to provide design and methodological knowledge, research, graphic and visual design, aimed at a full understanding of current fashion trends, the most famous and prestigious brands on the international scene. Meet professors with strong academic and professional experience gained in the most important companies in the industry, capable of transmitting visual strategies and aesthetic principles of the brand in line with current corporate standards to enhance your aesthetic sensitivity and express your creative and communicative abilities to the fullest.INFO REQUEST\r\nMain topics\r\n\r\nFashion\r\nStyling\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Fashion Styling\r\n 	Visual Communication\r\n 	Trend Analysis and Research\r\n\r\n\r\nPhotography\r\nand Presentation\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Concept Design\r\n 	Shooting\r\n 	Portfolio\r\n\r\n\r\nFashion\r\nMultimedia\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Fashion Editing\r\n 	Social Communication\r\n 	Visual analysis\r\n\r\n\r\nBrand\r\nCommunication\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Copywriting\r\n 	Contemporary Fashion\r\n 	Brand Identity\r\n\r\n\r\nDiscover the Fashion Stylist profession\r\nThe Fashion Stylist is a creative and expert professional in the field of fashion, whose main role is to design and coordinate the visual image of individuals, models, celebrities, or fashion products for companies. They are professionals with a deep understanding of current fashion trends, various brands, and their stylistic choices. The focal point of their activity is collaboration with photographers, fashion editors, art directors, and clients to ensure that the creative vision is interpreted correctly and translated into high-quality fashion images.The ability to communicate effectively, attention to detail, and a developed artistic sensibility are key elements to excel in this profession. Versatility and creativity are essential to adapt to the needs and specific requests of each project, thus contributing to the success of the visual communication of fashion houses.INFO REQUEST\r\nTarget audience\r\nThe course is designed for anyone who wishes to acquire knowledge and skills in visual communication design. It is suitable for those who want to develop their creativity and learn the fundamental techniques for designing and coordinating visual images in the fashion industry.\r\nEducational aim\r\nThe course aims to train a highly qualified figure in the field of visual and digital communication, capable of using appropriate languages and tools to anticipate and meet customer requests through their vision of fashion and aesthetic taste. The course aims to ensure adequate mastery of artistic methods and techniques, as well as the acquisition of specific disciplinary and professional skills, to provide students with design and expressive knowledge and methodologies in the use of representation tools and artistic practices, with particular attention to fashion.\r\nAdmission requirements\r\n\r\n\r\n 	High school diplomaÂ or another degree obtained abroad confirmingÂ 12 years of schooling.\r\n 	Official translation of the diplomaÂ andÂ transcriptsÂ (if not already in Italian or English).\r\n 	Motivational letter.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 	High school diplomaÂ or another degree obtained abroad confirmingÂ 12 years of schooling, recognized through a âDeclaration of ValueÂ (DV)â.\r\n 	Official translation of the diplomaÂ andÂ transcriptsÂ (if not already in Italian or English).\r\n 	Italian language certification B2Â â students without a language certification will be supported before the start of the course to acquire the required certification.\r\n 	Passing the admission tests.\r\n 	Residence permit/application for a residence permit, to be submitted to the orientation office within 8 working days of arrival in Italy.\r\n 	Motivational letter.\r\n\r\nThe course in Fashion Styling and Communication can open doors to various career opportunities, including:Your role will be to shape the visual image through the art of combining clothing, accessories, and makeup. Collaborate with photographers and art directors to create visual stories that reflect the brand.Responsible for curating the image of public figures through the choice of clothing and accessories. Collaborate with agents and stylists to ensure that celebrities wear looks that reflect their personality and fit current trends.Responsible for the visual vision of creative projects. Collaborate with designers, photographers, and other creatives to ensure visual harmony. Your guidance will contribute to defining the visual identity of a brand or project.Provide advice on personal style, fashion, and image. Collaborate with individual clients or companies, helping them improve their outward appearance, self-esteem, and professional presentation.You will be responsible for creating visual and written content that supports marketing strategies. Your work will contribute to creating a captivating brand image and engaging the audience through various platforms.Your task will be to curate and oversee editorial content related to fashion. You will collaborate with writers, photographers, and stylists to create publications that reflect trends and inspire the audience.\r\nREQUEST INFORMATION\r\nFill in the form and we will get back to you as soon as possible.\r\nWould you prefer to speak directly with our Orientation Team?\r\nClick here and book a personalised interview.\r\', 'Fashion Styling and Communication', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fashio-stylist-image-consultant-two-year-course', '', '', '2024-11-13 16:33:12', '2024-11-13 15:33:12', '', 