(281, 3, '2019-05-17 10:11:40', '2019-05-17 08:11:40', '\r\nSHORT COURSE IN PATTERN-MAKING AND TAILORING\r\n\r\nSHORT COURSE IN PATTERN-MAKING AND TAILORING\r\nSummer Course - Milan\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBoth the duration of the course and the number of patterns designed depend on the chosen attendance and the program (40,\r\n80 or 120 hours) and on the studentâs personal skills and learning speed.\r\nThe course in Pattern-making and Tailoring provide you a 360Â° overview on the methodology and work planning inside a\r\npattern office or tailoring lab, through direct classes in the class. The program consists of onsite technical and practical classes.\r\nYou will be able to test your technical and practical skills, moving the first steps in the amazing world of Tailoring.\r\nStudents will be shown all the phases of the job, from the analysis of the technical sheet to the study of the Silhouette, from the\r\nstudy of the wearability and measures to the main techniques for designing a paper pattern, from the placement on the fabric to\r\nthe cut, sewing and finishing.\r\nAt the end, all participants will be given an Attendance Certificate.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCourse details:\r\nLocation: Milan\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCourse duration: 40Â hours\r\n\r\nCost of the course: â¬1464\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCourse duration:Â 80 hours\r\n\r\nCost of the course: â¬2440\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCourse duration:Â 120 hours\r\n\r\nCost of the course: â¬3294\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe cost includes texts and handouts, the registration fee and 22% VAT\r\nDESTINATARI\r\nThe summer course is aimed at both beginners and those who want to quickly assess their skills and evaluate whether to continue their training in the fashion industry as Pattern Makers or Tailors.\r\nSTUDY PLAN\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Introduction to Pattern-Making\r\n 	Study of the Silhouettes\r\n 	Study of the Patterns\r\n 	Study of the Wearability\r\n 	Study of the Measures\r\n 	Standard Sizes\r\n 	Tailor-making\r\n 	Sartorial Pattern-Making\r\n 	Pattern-Drawing\r\n 	Pattern-Developing\r\n 	Cut\r\n 	Placement\r\n 	Sewing\r\n 	Prototyping with fabrics\r\n 	Finishing touches\r\n\r\nASK FOR ', 'Pattern-making and tailoring', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pattern-making-and-tailoring', '', '', '2023-11-15 15:57:35', '2023-11-15 14:57:35', '', 0, 'https://www.ferrarifashionschool.it/corso-modellistica-e-sartoria-base/', 0, 'page', '', 0);
