rdless their notoriety.\r\n\r\nThe Pattern-maker realizes the outfit drawn by the fashion designer, by developing patterns, from designing to realizing the collection, respecting proportions and the style from the sketches.\r\n\r\nHe/she selects the fabrics, the accessories and then, once drawn the pattern, checks the wearability of the garment, corrects any possible flaw and follows the production.FIND OUT MORE\r\nMASTERS AND SHORT COURSES\r\n\r\nI WORKSHOP DEL MOMENTO\r\n\r\nNEWS\r\', 'Tailoring', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tailoring', '', '', '2020-01-20 12:40:15', '2020-01-20 11:40:15', '', 0, 'https://www.ferrarifashionschool.it/?page_id=2974', 0, 'page', '', 0),
