(317, 3, '2020-01-21 11:21:18', '2020-01-21 10:21:18', '\r\nI Computer design\r\n\r\nCOMPUTER DESIGN FOR FASHION\r\nShort Course - Milan\r\nThe Computer Design Course allows each student to learn how to use tools and graphic softwares such as Adobe Photoshop and Illustrator, for Photo editing, Graphic Design, Presentations, Portfolio etc ..\r\n\r\nAdobe Photoshop is the fundamental software for those who need to deal with, manipulate and process digital images. Actually, Photoshop has a wide variety of tools and functions that make it extremely versatile. This is why Photoshop has proved to be the essential tool for those who work in the field of Design and Digital Imaging.\r\n\r\nAdobe Illustrator is a program used by both digital artists and graphic designers to create vector images. These images will then be used for logos, illustrations, tables, charts, diagrams, flyers, business cards, posters, large format prints, layouts for websites or applications and much more.\r\n\r\nAdobe InDesign is a software for editorial post-production aimed to professional publishing. It allows to quickly create layout for projects for printing, web and mobile.\r\nCourse details:\r\n\r\n 	Location: Milan\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 	From July 2021\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Duration: 2 weeks\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Total cost: â¬ 1769\r\n\r\nThe price includes VAT and enrolment fee.\r\nTARGET\r\nDesigners, Fashion designers, graphic designers, photographers and anyone, working in the field of digital images, either for work or passion, who want to make use of them for editing and creating their portfolio in a highly professional way.Â \r\n\r\nThe course is dedicated to people over 18 year old. It is not necessary to have experience as our programs are dedicated to those who start from zero or with little experience through individual lessons and customized exercises, according to the starting level and individual learning time.\r\n\r\nIn our three-year courses for Fashion Design and Fashion Designer - Portfolio, the Computer Design Course is included in the study program.\r\nTRAINING GOALS\r\nThe main purpose of the course is to train a complete professional figure able to managing the entire production cycle, from the conception to the concrete realization, through a personalized educational path.\r\nSTUDY PROGRAMS\r\n\r\n\r\n 	INTRODUCTION TO THE USE OF GRAPHIC SOFTWARE FOR CREATING A COLLECTION PLAN AND / OR PORTFOLIO\r\n 	DESIGN METHODOLOGY:\r\n\r\n 	Moodboard creation\r\n 	Portfolio\r\n 	Graphics for publishing\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 	PHOTOSHOP: PRACTICAL EXERCISES\r\n 	ILLUSTRATOR: PRACTICAL EXERCISES\r\n 	INDESIGN: PRACTICAL EXERCISES\r\n\r\nRICHIEDI ALTRE ', 'Computer design', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'computer-design', '', '', '2020-10-23 09:26:40', '2020-10-23 07:26:40', '', 2970, 'https://www.ferrarifashionschool.it/?page_id=2985', 0, 'page', '', 0),
