(398, 3, '2023-11-22 14:41:40', '2023-11-22 13:41:40', '\r\nInternational relations\r\n\r\nStarting in 2015, Ferrari Fashion School has taken a path of internationalisation with the aim of establishing relations and exchanges with institutions in the same or related sector all over the world.\r\nThe fashion industry is one of the largest and fastest growing globally, with an estimated market value of around $3 trillion per year. Enabling students to supplement their education with an international experience can help them better understand global trends and industry challenges, as well as develop the skills needed to operate in an increasingly interconnected market.\r\n\r\nThrough the internationalisation process, the Academy aims to provide a high level of industry technical, cultural and language skills that are increasingly in demand by fashion companies working with suppliers and customers all over the world.\r\n\r\nIn 2023, Ferrari Fashion School received international accreditation from Teesside University.\r\n\r\nIn order to expand collaborations, contacts have been made with the following institutions, operating in different countries around the world, in the fashion and design sector:\r\n\r\n 	Parson The New School\r\n 	Fashion Institute of Technology\r\n 	Aschan Studio\r\n 	Universidad Europea\r\n 	Pearl Academy\r\n 	JD Institute of Technology\r\n 	LeÂ MarkÂ School of Art\r\n 	Keimyung University\r\n 	Kyungpook National University\r\n 	Teesside University\r\n\r\nThe Academy encourages and supports students in seeking an internship abroad through the Admission &amp; Career Service office as it believes that international mobility plays a crucial role in building a more complete and competitive professional profile.', 'International relations', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'international-relations', '', '', '2024-02-22 16:10:03', '2024-02-22 15:10:03', '', 0, 'https://ferrarifashionschool.it/?page_id=6827', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(399, 3, '2023-11-22 15:19:33', '2023-11-22 14:19:33', '\r\nCoordinators\r\n\r\nUndergraduate Courses\r\n\r\nFashion Design\r\nProf.ssa Giuseppina Liguori\r\n\r\nFashion Stylist &amp; Communication\r\nProf. Riccardo Carrapa\r\n\r\nFashion Business &amp; Digital Marketing\r\nProf.ssa Carolina Guajana\r\n\r\nFashion &amp; Textile Design\r\nProf.ssa Giuseppina Liguori\r\n\r\nTailoring and Pattern Making\r\nProf.ssa Eva Rondinelli\r\n\r\nMaster Courses\r\n\r\n\r\nFashion Photography &amp; Fashion films | Fashion Stylist &amp; Art Direction\r\nProf. Riccardo Carrapa\r\n\r\nCourse Leader - Undergraduate courses\r\n\r\n\r\nBA (Hons) Fashion Design\r\nProf. Riccardo Carrapa\r\n\r\nBA (Hons) Fashion Business &amp; Digital Marketing\r\nProf.ssa Carolina Guajana\r\n\r\n', 'Coordinators', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'coordinators', '', '', '2024-02-22 14:57:47', '2024-02-22 13:57:47', '', 0, 'https://ferrarifashionschool.it/?page_id=6787', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(400, 3, '2023-11-22 15:26:37', '2023-11-22 14:26:37', '\r\nTutor\r\nThe FFS tutoring service guides and assists students throughout their studies, involving them in the educational process, in order to overcome any obstacles that may arise in their academic progress. This is aimed at making their studies effective and productive.\r\n\r\nIn the first steps of the student\'s career, the tutor helps to ease the transition from secondary school to academia and continues over the years with the aim of assisting the student and improving the quality of learning, providing, among other things, advice on building the curriculum and further education activities.\r\n\r\nOnce the course of study is over, the tutor\'s task becomes that of advising new graduates on how to successfully enter the world of work, in synergy with the Career Service office, for those training apprenticeship activities offered by the SBB.', 'Tutor', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tutor', '', '', '2024-03-12 17:33:51', '2024-03-12 16:33:51', '', 0, 'https://ferrarifashionschool.it/?page_id=6805', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(401, 3, '2023-11-22 15:42:22', '2023-11-22 14:42:22', '\r\nStudent Experience\r\n\r\nFashion Shows\r\nand Events\r\nFerrari Fashion School offers its students the exclusive opportunity to showcase their talent and gain international visibility by participating in prestigious events such as Fuorisalone, Milan Fashion Week and many others, as well as promoting events and fashion shows dedicated to promoting their talents.\r\n\r\nIn a world where promotion and access to high-level events have high costs, Ferrari Fashion School offers an opportunity that is unique in Italy: selected students can enjoy free use of a showroom located in the heart of Milan\'s Design District, take part in dedicated events and fashion shows and receive the support they need to organise and promote their projects in the best possible way.\r\n\r\nStudying at Ferrari Fashion School means becoming part of an institution that believes in the potential of young talents and is committed to accompanying them throughout their training. Students have the opportunity to put themselves to the test, confront themselves directly with the public and the market, and develop the skills they need to succeed in a highly competitive sector.\r\nProject with companies\r\nFerrari Fashion School offers its students the opportunity to collaborate with important Italian and international brands and companies, participating in numerous interdisciplinary projects, promoted during their training. The aim is to offer them the opportunity to deal directly with the labour market and with professionals in the sector, in order to enrich their cultural background and experience in the field, with a view to embarking on a career in the world of fashion and luxury.\r\nCultural activities\r\nFerrari Fashion School offers a variety of cultural activities including lectures, master classes, workshops and seminars, meetings with professionals, guided tours of exhibitions and museums, and many other activities that can stimulate students\' creativity and inspiration, providing them with the opportunity to explore the world of creative arts in a deeper and more meaningful way.\r\nStudents Experience\r\nFerrari Fashion School allows its students to live a unique experience that can enrich them not only professionally but also humanly.\r\nJoining Ferrari Fashion School means being part of a network of professionals recognised and esteemed by the market all over the world and having the opportunity to forge important relationships useful for one\'s personal and professional growth.\r\nAttention to the student, to his or her artistic growth, to the development of talent and creative identity, as well as constant support from the academy\'s teachers and staff, are fundamental elements that accompany the student throughout his or her training.\r\n\r\nStudying at Ferrari Fashion School is an experience aimed at transmitting important values to our students, which will accompany them in the future throughout their careers.\r\nREQUEST INFORMATION\r\nFill in the form and we will get back to you as soon as possible.\r\nWould you prefer to speak directly with our Orientation Team?\r\nClick here and book a personalised interview.\r\', 'Student Experience', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'experience', '', '', '2024-03-12 17:28:13', '2024-03-12 16:28:13', '', 0, 'https://ferrarifashionschool.it/?page_id=7652', 0, 'page', '', 0);
