(402, 3, '2023-11-22 15:56:05', '2023-11-22 14:56:05', '\r\nBachelor of Arts\r\nFashion Business\r\nand Psychology\r\n\r\nCourse Details\r\nLocation: Milan\r\n\r\nDuration: 3 academic years\r\n\r\nStart: October 2025\r\n\r\nCredits: 360 UK credits - 180 ECTS\r\n\r\nClass size: max 15 students\r\n\r\nLanguage: English\r\n\r\n Award Title: BA (Hons) Fashion Business and Psychology\r\n\r\nEducational Partner: Teesside University\r\nThe Bachelor of Arts with Honours in Fashion Business and Psychology, integrates the study of business and neuromarketing within the context of the fashion industry.\r\nIt provides a comprehensive view of the fashion system and emphasizes the role of consumer psychology in the marketing strategies of fashion and luxury companies. Led by expert lecturers and utilizing state-of-the-art technology, this multidisciplinary course offers a practical and innovative experience. Transform your career in the fashion industry, where creativity and neuroscience converge to define the future of business.\r\n\r\nThis course is validated by Teesside Universitrd the degree upon completion of the program.INFO REQUEST\r\nMain topics\r\n\r\nStrategic\r\nMarketing\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Fashion Marketing\r\n 	Business Strategy\r\n 	Market Research\r\n\r\n\r\nPsychology\r\nin Fashion\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Fashion Psychology\r\n 	Consumer Behaviors\r\n 	Neuromarketing\r\n\r\n\r\nDigital\r\nBranding\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Digital Marketing\r\n 	Fashion and Beauty Advertising\r\n 	Fashion Branding\r\n\r\n\r\nCustomer\r\nExperience\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Licensing and Co-branding\r\n 	Customer Experience\r\n 	Colors Psychology\r\n\r\n\r\nCourse Features\r\nIn this course, you will acquire knowledge about the latest marketing techniques, strategies, and tools, combined with neuroscientific insights applied in the fashion and luxury industry. We will explore various relevant topics, including behavioral economics, consumer psychology, digital content and marketing, customer experience, fashion communication, and retail management. Designed for aspiring professionals, the course is characterized by its practical and multidisciplinary nature, complemented by the analysis of real case studies and challenging projects.With a faculty of industry experts and fashion business professionals, the course provides in-depth guidance in understanding neuromarketing as applied to the fashion context. The groundbreaking career prospects for graduates reflect the course\'s comprehensive and innovative approach in preparing students for success in the highly competitive fashion industry.INFO REQUEST\r\nTarget audience\r\nThe course is designed for fashion enthusiasts who aspire to pursue a path where business, psychology, and marketing converge to create an expert professional ready to address business needs. It is ideal for students seeking to update their skills and acquire a more advanced and interdisciplinary perspective on business management in the fashion world.\r\nEducational aim\r\nThe course aims to offer a robust education in the field of fashion business, seamlessly integrated with insights into neuromarketing. Students will acquire multidisciplinary skills to comprehend consumer behavior by applying neuroscientific principles to marketing strategies in the fashion industry. Educational objectives include the ability to analyze neuroscientific data, develop innovative branding strategies, and understand the psychological dynamics that drive purchasing decisions.\r\nAdmission requirements\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Upper secondary school diploma or an equivalent qualification obtained abroad, confirming 12 years of schooling.\r\n 	Students whose mother tongue is not English must demonstrate language proficiency equivalent to an IELTS score of at least 5.5. Students lacking language proficiency will receive support prior to the start of the course.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n 	Upper secondary school diploma or an equivalent qualification obtained abroad confirming 12 years of schooling.\r\n 	Official translation of the qualification and transcripts (if not already in Italian or English).\r\n 	Passing the national university entrance examination, if required in the candidate\'s country of origin.\r\n 	Students whose mother tongue is not English must demonstrate language proficiency equivalent to an IELTS score of at least 5.5. Students lacking language proficiency will receive support before the start of the course.\r\n 	Residence permit/application for a residence permit to be submitted to the guidance office within 8 working days of arrival in Italy.\r\n\r\nFor additional and detailed information regarding entry requirements based on your country of origin, we invite you  to visit the Teesside University website.\r\nThe Bachelor degree in Fashion Business and Psychology can unlock numerous career opportunities, including:Responsible for conducting in-depth market research to assess business opportunities, analyzing demographic data, market trends, and competitors to provide key insights influencing business decisions.Utilizing neuroscience principles to understand how the brain responds to marketing stimuli, you will optimize communication and promotion strategies for a deeper and more effective impact on target audiences.Handling the business and strategic aspects of the fashion industry, collaborating with multidisciplinary teams to ensure the commercial success of the company\'s product lines, considering financial, logistical, and market aspects.Conducting in-depth analysis of consumer behavior using research methodologies to understand preferences, motivations, and purchasing patterns. Your insights will guide company strategies to adapt products and services to consumer needs.Serving as the point of reference for online marketing strategies, utilizing skills in SEO, SEM, social media, and content marketing to increase your company\'s online visibility. Your role will be crucial in implementing digital campaigns that generate tangible results.Responsible for brand management and promotion, coordinating marketing campaigns to ensure consistency in the brand image.Designing immersive experiences in physical shops, creating environments that reflect the brand identity and enhance the customer shopping experience.\r\nREQUEST INFORMATION\r\nFill in the form and we will get back to you as soon as possible.\r\nWould you prefer to speak directly with our Orientation Team?\r\nClick here and book a personalised interview.\r\', 'Bachelor of Arts Fashion Business and Psychology', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fashion-business-psychology', '', '', '2025-02-10 22:16:02', '2025-02-10 21:16:02', '', 0, 'https://ferrarifashionschool.it/?page_id=6443', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(403, 3, '2023-11-22 17:41:39', '2023-11-22 16:41:39', '\r\nOpen Day\r\nFerrari Fashion School\r\n\r\n\r\nFor those who dream of a present in fashion.\r\nFerrari Fashion School presents its Triennial and Master\'s programs in two online events, one in Italian and one in English. Choose which event to attend and register through the form.\r\nOnline Open Day for International students\r\nJanuary 20, 2025, we look forward to seeing you online at 3 p.m.\r\nOnline Open Day for Italian students\r\nJanuary 24, 2025, we expect you online at 3:00 pm.\r\nBOOK NOW\r\n\r\nFor today\'s fashion dreamers.\r\nJoin our Open Days and become a real professional by studying together with real experts in the fashion industry.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Open Day\r\nFerrari Fashion School organizes Open Days to introduce about itself and make itself known to students interested in the world of fashion and who dream of becoming fashion designers, stylists, luxury management, marketing managers or photographers in the fashion world.\r\nStudents will have the opportunity to meet the teachers and course leaders of the course of interest, and discover Ferrari Fashion School\'s extracurricular activities starting with external visits, collaborations with companies and professionals.\r\nDuring the Open Day, students can also receive support from the Guidance team to better understand which course is best suited to specialize their path in the areas of fashion design, styling, business, modeling, communication and fashion photography.\r\nThe Program\r\n\r\nDISCOVER OUR BACHELORS AND MASTERS\r\nParticipating in the Ferrari Fashion School Open Day is very easy. Check the program below to choose the course that interests you and start yout path of your fashion future.\r\n&nbsp;\r\nINSTITUTIONAL PRESENTATION - 3p.m. CET\r\nPRESENTATION OF BACHELOR AND BACHELOR OF ARTS\r\n\r\nBA Fashion Design\r\nBA Fashion Stylist and Communication\r\nBA Fashion Business and Digital Marketign\r\nBA Fashion Business and Psychology\r\n\r\nPRESENTATION OF MASTER AND MASTER OF ARTS\r\n\r\nFashion Styling and Art Direction\r\nFashion Photography and fashion Film\r\nMA Fashion Design and Creative Direction\r\nMA Fashion and Luxury Management\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you are in Italy and wish to follow the Open Day in presence please visit this page\r\nDISCOVER MORE\r\nWhy Participate?\r\n\r\nWe are not talking about just a simple open day.\r\nAttend a brief institutional presentation of the Academy, but most importantly, use the opportunity to actively immerse yourself in the Ferrari Fashion School experience from the very first moment. Learn about the programs, external visits, collaborations with companies of our Bachelors and Masters.BOOK NOW\r\nWhy Participate?\r\n\r\nWe are not talking about just a simple open day.\r\n\r\nAttend a brief institutional presentation of the Academy, but most importantly, use the opportunity to actively immerse yourself in the Ferrari Fashion School experience from the very first moment. Learn about the programs, external visits, collaborations with companies, and special projects of Ferrari Fashion School\'s.\r\n\r\nEducational Offer\r\n\r\nDiscover which course suits you best: test your talent and creativity.\r\n\r\n3 Year Course\r\nDesign della moda\r\nFashion Styling and Communication\r\n\r\nBachelor of Arts\r\nFashion Design\r\nFashion Styling and Communication\r\nFashion Business and Digital Marketing\r\nFashion Business and Psychology\r\n\r\nMaster\r\nFashion Styling and Art Direction\r\nFashion Photography and Fashion Film\r\n\r\nMaster of Arts\r\nFashion Design and Creative Direction\r\nFashion and Luxury Management\r\n\r\n\r\nFor those who dream of a present in fashion.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBook an Open Day\r\nJoin Ferrari Fashion School Milano\r\nand build your professional future with us.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\nBachelor of Arts\r\nThree-year Courses\r\nExplore with our team the BA and BSc courses at Ferrari Fashion School.\r\nChoose your preferred date and time and